reviewText: I am a counselor and have used this video with elementary age children a number of times.  They enjoyed it and I was able to use it's examples to spur discussion among the children.  Might not be the best out there, but it is certainly usable.
This is not the best DVD on prevention. Granted it was designed to reach a young audience. The stories are poorly staged. the colors are not that great. Disappointing.
